CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777017944
OL,3,CHealth data of 500,000 UK Biobank
OL,4,Cmembers offered for sale in data breach
OL,6,FThe details of 500,000 members of UK
OL,7,Fhealth information database Biobank
OL,8,Fhave been offered for sale online
OL,9,Ffollowing an internal data breach, the
OL,10,Fgovernment has confirmed.
OL,12,FThe UK Biobank charity informed the
OL,13,Fgovernment that they had identified a
OL,14,Fbreach of their data, and that it was
OL,15,Fbeing advertised for sale on Alibaba's
OL,16,Fe-commerce platforms in China,
OL,17,Ftechnology minister Ian Murray said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777017944
OL,3,CHealth data of 500,000 UK Biobank
OL,4,Cmembers offered for sale in data breach
OL,6,F"Biobank told us that three listings
OL,7,Fthat appear to sell Biobank
OL,8,Fparticipation data had been
OL,9,Fidentified. At least one of these
OL,10,Fthree datasets appeared to contain
OL,11,Fdata from all 500,000 UK Biobank
OL,12,Fvolunteers," Murray said.
OL,14,F"Additional listings offer support for
OL,15,Fapplying for legitimate access to UK
OL,16,FBiobank or analytical support for
OL,17,Fresearchers who already have access to
OL,18,Fthe data."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777017944
OL,3,CHealth data of 500,000 UK Biobank
OL,4,Cmembers offered for sale in data breach
OL,6,FThe Biobank is a collection of data
OL,7,Fthat has been used to achieve
OL,8,Fimprovements in the detection and
OL,9,Ftreatment of dementia, cancer and
OL,10,FParkinson's.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe data was breached internally, and
OL,18,Fdid not contain participants' names,
OL,19,Faddresses, contact details or
OL,20,Ftelephone numbers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777017944
OL,3,CHealth data of 500,000 UK Biobank
OL,4,Cmembers offered for sale in data breach
OL,6,FThe listings for the data were swiftly
OL,7,Fremoved from Alibaba before a sale was
OL,8,Fmade, Sir Rory Collins, CEO of UK
OL,9,FBiobank, said.
OL,11,F"The actions of these individuals are
OL,12,Fa clear breach of the contract they
OL,13,Fsigned with UK Biobank and they, along
OL,14,Fwith their academic institutions,
OL,15,Fimmediately had their access
OL,16,Fsuspended," Collins said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777017944
OL,3,CHealth data of 500,000 UK Biobank
OL,4,Cmembers offered for sale in data breach
OL,6,F"We apologise for the concern this
OL,7,Fwill cause and have already put in
OL,8,Fplace technology, processes and a
OL,9,Fboard-led review to stop this
OL,10,Fhappening again.
OL,12,F"We have also taken our research
OL,13,Fplatform offline whilst we add a
OL,14,Ffurther upgrade that helps prevent de-
OL,15,Fidentified data being taken out of the
OL,16,Fplatform. We expect this to take three
OL,17,Fweeks.
OL,19,F"Our existing plans to implement an
OL,20,Fautomated 'airlock' that checks files
OL,21,Fand data continues at pace."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777017944
OL,3,CHealth data of 500,000 UK Biobank
OL,4,Cmembers offered for sale in data breach
OL,6,FTechnology minister Murray also said
OL,7,FUK Biobank had referred itself to the
OL,8,FInformation Commissioner's Office.
OL,10,FHe told the Commons in a statement:
OL,11,F"Once the government was made aware of
OL,12,Fthe situation, we took immediate
OL,13,Faction to protect participants' data.
OL,14,FFirstly, we worked with Biobank, the
OL,15,FChinese government and the vendor, to
OL,16,Fensure that those three listings `
OL,17,Fthat UK Biobank informed us (of),
OL,18,Fincluding participant data ` had been
OL,19,Fremoved.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777017944
OL,3,CHealth data of 500,000 UK Biobank
OL,4,Cmembers offered for sale in data breach
OL,6,F"I want to thank the Chinese
OL,7,Fgovernment for the seriousness with
OL,8,Fwhich they work with us to help remove
OL,9,Fthese listings.
OL,11,F"Secondly, we ensured that the Biobank
OL,12,Fcharity revoked access to three
OL,13,Fresearch institutions identified as
OL,14,Fthe source of that information.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777017944
OL,3,CHealth data of 500,000 UK Biobank
OL,4,Cmembers offered for sale in data breach
OL,6,F"And thirdly, we have asked that the
OL,7,FBiobank charity pause further access
OL,8,Fto its data until they put in place a
OL,9,Ftechnical solution to prevent data
OL,10,Ffrom its current platform from being
OL,11,Fdownloaded in this way again. I can
OL,12,Fconfirm to the House that this pause
OL,13,Fis now in place.
OL,15,F"UK Biobank have also referred
OL,16,Fthemselves to the Information
OL,17,FCommissioner's Office."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUyD@WO]
